Review Title: The facility was adequate, but shabby. Staff was mostly indifferent to us.
Negative Reviews: This hotel was meant to be high end when it was built, but has descended to shabbiness.  The hardscapes - tiles, counters, floors and lighting are all beautiful, but the maintenance of the surfaces has not been kept up.  There was mold in the caulking around the bathtub.  I found a finger or toenail clipping in the carpet near the bed (YUK!) I noticed that there were scuff marks and signs of wear and tear on the trims. The clerk who checked us in was indifferent to us, not friendly at all.  Breakfast was good, but I would have liked to have some fresh fruit.
